######################################################################
NOTE:
Any strings with spaces in them must be surounded by single quotes 
i.e. 'Will Snelson' not Will Snelson.
######################################################################

Products:
Filter by name:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product filter=name:Gas;

Filter by type:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product filter=type:insurance;

Filter by price:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product filter=price:12.50-35;

Order by price ascending:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product sort=ascending:true;

Order by price descending:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product sort=descending:true;

Order by product name alphabetically:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product sort=alphabetically:true;

Filter and Sort by any example:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=product sort=alphabetically:true filter=type:insurance,name:'Landlord Insurance';

Customer Accounts:
Filter by name
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account filter=name:'Will Snelson';

Filter by postcode:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account filter=postcode:SK103QF;

Order by product name alphabetically:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account sort=alphabetically:true;

Order by number of orders ascending:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account sort=numberOfOrders:ascending;

Order by number of orders descending:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account sort=numberOfOrders:descending;

Filter and Sort by any example:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=account sort=alphabetically:true filter=postcode:SK103QF;

Suppliers:
Filter by name:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=supplier filter=name:Vodafone;

Filter by products stocked:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=supplier filter=productsStocked:true;

Order by product name alphabetically:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=supplier sort=alphabetically:true;

Filter and Sort by any example:
java -jar techtest-1-jar-with-dependencies.jar doctype=supplier sort=alphabetically:true filter=productsStocked:true;
